Wind: They ride the wind (Kunark evacs), and can stun/damage their enemies with the wind.<br>
Fire: They can burn their enemies.<br>
Water: They can freeze their enemies, and can stop the rain.<br>
Earth: They can root their enemies, and can cause earthquakes.<br>
Though the masters of nature would be more appropriate for them. <p>~~
