<br>
That's just crazy talk.  I play both a mid-level mage and a level 51 wizard, and I think you're giving wizards a raw deal here.<br>
<br>
First of all, their pets aren't pets.  It's just the graphical representation of a buff, and a crappy buff at that.  Only at level 49 does the mana regen kick in, and it's 1 point per tick.  Pathetic.  The familiar doesn't fight, take aggro, or basically do _anything_ to help you in an encounter other than provide a few resist points.  For a mage to gripe about the wizard familiar is ridiculous.<br>
<br>
Secondly, please don't compare wizards to druids in terms of being &quot;cheap&quot;.  On the contrary, wizards are one of the hardest classes to play.  There is no way you could call wizards &quot;cheap&quot; if you had played one for fifteen minutes.  Yes, the nukes are big and fast, but you can't use 'em to their fullest extent--because you'll end up getting aggro.  When a wizard gets aggro, there's no pet to help out.  There's nothing but a soft caster skull ripe for the crackin'.  As well, any wizard who tries to solo before level 29 has a deathwish.<br>
<br>
I love playing my mage, because, frankly, it's a cakewalk compared to playing my wizard.  I easily kill MOBs and survive encounters that would have sent my poor wizard on a corpse run in the first fifteen seconds.  While it's true that I have yet to go on any high level encounters with my mage, I have a very long memory, and thus far the mage has been staggeringly more powerful and successful than my wizard.<br>
<br>
Trust me, if there's any class that can sympathize with the frustrations of magicians, it's their wizard brethren.  Why waste your time hating them when there are so many druids running around? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uroalin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Roalin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#333333>(2/11/02 10:21:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=135.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: lvl 54 Mage wants to Rant about Mages </span><hr size=1> One more note:<br>
